Ability.Name: Firaxian Shark Repellent
Ability.Description: A sprayable repellent for Firaxian Sharks. Can be used on allies or enemies, with differing effects. Enemy Target: Spray repellent into the eyes of a nearby opponent, ignoring the strongly worded warning label. Momentarily stuns the opponent, and blinds them for 9s. Friendly Target: Spray repellent on an ally. Reduces the aggro range of Firaxian Sharks within 50m by 80%. Upon taking damage from a Firaxian Shark, reduces threat against that attacker by 80%. Effects last 4h.

Ability.Name: Jetpack Reposition
Ability.Description: Jet Charges to the outer edge of a quadrant of the arena that you're not already in (selected at random). Does no damage, but gets you out of a bad situation!

Ability.Name: Stunning Mine
Ability.Description: Throws a stunning mine on the ground at target location. After a 3s delay, the mine will arm. The first target that comes within 4m of the armed mine will be stunned for 4s. This ability can hit friendly targets. Placed mines remain for up to 2 minutes. A maximum of 6 mines can be placed simultaneously.

Ability.Description: Binds the target in a stasis field for up to 8 seconds. Damage to the target causes this effect to end prematurely. Targets may only be affected by Electro-Stasis once every 30 seconds. Target must not be suffering from periodic damage and have greater than 90% max health.

Ability.Description: Places a Kolto-powered shield around the target, preventing a moderate amount of damage for up to 20 seconds.

Ability.Name: Anti-Personnel Detonator
Ability.Description: Activates an explosive that deals <<1>> kinetic damage to up to 5 enemies 5m around the user. Generates a moderate amount of threat and reduces incoming damage by 50% for 10 seconds. Does not hit sleeping, lifted, or incapacitated enemies.

Ability.Description: Fires a multi-grapple line that fires in a wide cone in front of the companion and pulls the closest three targets and generates a high amount of threat. Only affects targets that are in combat and are not in cover or have Boss Immunity.

Ability.Name: Smoke Shift

Ability.Name: Affliction

Electrocutes the target, dealing minor energy damage and stunning it for 2.5 seconds.
NOTE - Balanced for Caster NPCs, due to the length of the stun.

Ability.Name: Force Lightning
Ability.Description: Deals high energy damage to the target over the duration of the effect. Force Lightning also slows the movement speed of the target by 50%. Balanced for Caster NPCs.

Followers will "Gang Up" on targets stunned in this manner. Additional deployed squads will pile onto abducted targets. If the leader of a squad is destroyed, their followers will also be destroyed.
